        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The air cleaner air intake duct has been modified to improve the durability of the duct to air
                    cleaner housing connection for 2500 and 2600 Models built from September 1993 through August 1994
                    with DT 466 and 530 International engines, and from January 1994 through August 1994 on the above
                    vehicles with all other engines. The following parts and service procedure is to make this
                    modification.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
